on Pro'; font-size:12pt">demonstrate t</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">he ability to meet the safety and installation standards in BS 7671</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic">Wiring Regulations</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">and requirements in the Building Regulations</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">.</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> The minimum competences required </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">under the </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">Electrotechnical Assessment Specification</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">are those that would be needed to obta</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">in a Level 3 qualification in electrical installations in dwellings. </span></li></ol><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 18pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><ol start="9" type="1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 32pt; padding-left:4pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">Update</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">d</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">competence </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">training </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">is </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">required</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> </span><