nt-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">not only to keep their membership lists up to date and publish them on their own websites but also </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">to supply </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">them </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">for inclusion</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">in the </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">general </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">C</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">ompetent </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">P</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">erson </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">R</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">egister</span><a name="_ftnref8"></a><a href="#_ftn8">[8]</a><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">.</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> </span></li></ol><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><ol start="22" type="1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">Scheme operators are required to use an agreed mechanism to make available to other scheme operators the names of former members whose membership has been terminated by the scheme and the reason for termination.  (All members have to be made aware of this </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">condition on initial registration and renewal of membership.)</span></li></ol><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p 